N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 2100.6 - Filing of amendments

State Regulations

Such amendment or revocation shall be filed with the

Secretary of State and shall take effect upon the date of filing unless
otherwise specified therein. Notes
